    </p>
    <button
      class="border-foreground cursor-pointer rounded-xl border px-[1em] py-[0.1em] text-base"
      id="sortButton"
    >
      Sort it</button
    >
    <button
      class="border-foreground cursor-pointer rounded-xl border px-[1em] py-[0.1em] text-base"
      id="resetButton"
